40:08.625 --> 40:10.226
A thousand gold denarii?

40:10.250 --> 40:11.250
Two.

40:13.541 --> 40:14.541
Two?

40:16.541 --> 40:17.351
Denarii.

40:17.375 --> 40:18.375
Mmm.

40:34.833 --> 40:35.833
Stand back!

40:36.500 --> 40:37.683
Stand back!

40:39.083 --> 40:44.433
My emperors, lords,
ladies and gentlemen, and senators,

40:45.000 --> 40:49.808
for your
entertainment, the art of combat.

40:52.333 --> 40:59.683
May I present the barbarian
versus from my own stable, the mighty Vitek!

41:00.083 --> 41:01.641
[crowd cheering]

41:07.750 --> 41:08.750
This is your radiator.

41:09.208 --> 41:11.308
It is.

41:13.583 --> 41:16.725
Three rounds, hand to hand. Swords!

41:18.166 --> 41:20.516
We want swords to fight to the death.

41:22.541 --> 41:26.933
No quarter to be
offered or given. Fight now.

41:29.708 --> 41:32.808
Brother, I am the king of the gods.

41:35.583 --> 41:36.808
Let's not kill each
other for their amusement.

42:08.958 --> 42:13.309
[crowd cheering]

42:13.333 --> 42:13.767
[yelling]

