Help, Jesus!

56:19.458 --> 56:20.684
(explosions)

56:20.708 --> 56:25.558
(cheering)

56:31.000 --> 56:37.350
Hold together and when
the charges break for the wall.

56:38.166 --> 56:39.166
Why should I?

56:41.750 --> 56:45.808
(explosions) Hold, hold!

56:48.791 --> 56:49.791
Cows!

56:51.291 --> 57:00.333
(explosions)

57:00.375 --> 57:00.434
(cheering)

57:00.458 --> 57:06.684
(explosions)

57:06.708 --> 57:06.767
