58:34.791 --> 58:35.726
(explosions)

58:35.750 --> 58:48.791
(yelling) (yelling)

58:48.875 --> 58:51.559
(explosions)

58:51.583 --> 59:01.000
(yelling)

59:01.916 --> 59:04.350
Brother, is that poet, is it not?

59:05.833 --> 59:06.833
I can't remember.

59:07.916 --> 59:08.916
That night was a blur.

59:10.833 --> 59:13.600
The gates of hell are open night and day.

59:14.500 --> 59:16.266
Smooth as I forget.

59:17.333 --> 59:18.350
Smooth as the scent.

59:19.750 --> 59:20.808
Smooth as the scent.

59:22.208 --> 59:23.208
Easy as the way.

59:31.250 --> 59:32.250
Kill!

59:33.708 --> 59:34.708
(explosions)

