01:01:53.833 --> 01:01:55.683
The road to freedom
doesn't run through the arena.

01:01:57.250 --> 01:01:58.250
Leads to this.

01:02:03.541 --> 01:02:04.541
Go to yourself.

01:02:06.166 --> 01:02:12.059
