01:43:15.583 --> 01:43:16.583
The dream?

01:43:17.208 --> 01:43:18.208
The dream of Rome?

01:43:19.166 --> 01:43:20.516
It's an old man's fantasy.

01:43:22.500 --> 01:43:23.641
Who are you?

01:43:25.791 --> 01:43:29.475
