01:43:35.250 --> 01:43:36.250
I have a destiny.

01:43:40.416 --> 01:43:42.100
The gods delivered you to me.

01:43:44.625 --> 01:43:46.808
You will be my instrument.

01:43:47.500 --> 01:43:49.725
