01:47:40.041 --> 01:47:40.726
Give it to me.

01:47:40.750 --> 01:47:41.976
You always lie.

01:47:42.000 --> 01:47:44.892
Give it to me.

01:47:44.916 --> 01:47:47.308
Look at me.

01:47:47.708 --> 01:47:48.601
Look at me.

01:47:48.625 --> 01:47:49.625
