your father's mark on me?

01:56:20.625 --> 01:56:21.683
If there is anything,

01:56:23.125 --> 01:56:25.766
if there is anything you need,

01:56:27.916 --> 01:56:29.266
in these last hours,

01:56:30.625 --> 01:56:31.625
