01:57:26.583 --> 01:57:27.583
Ride to Ostia.

01:57:29.000 --> 01:57:31.850
Take this ring to General
Darius Sextus, are you listening?

01:57:33.458 --> 01:57:34.891
Darius Sextus?

01:57:35.625 --> 01:57:37.558
